PKG_LONGDESC="Cython (http://cython.org) is a language that makes writing C extensions for \
the Python language as easy as Python itself.  Cython is based on the \
well-known Pyrex, but supports more cutting edge functionality and \
Kivy is an open source, cross-platform Python framework"
